<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Evolve music</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/skeleton.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="bundle.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Evolve music</h1>
    <p>Please tell me how do you like those pieces (1 = worst, 5 = best).</p>
    <p>Give it some time and we will together breed music of your taste.</p>
    <form action="/" method="post">
        <ul class="music-form__rank_list">
            <% for(let sound = 0; sound < 3; sound++) {%>
            <li class="rank_list--item">
                <h2 class="rank_list--heading">Soundtrack <%= sound + 1 %></h2>
                <p><a id="play-button-<%= sound %>" class="play-button">&#8987; Loading sound&#8230;</a></p>
                <ul class="music-form__rank-box">
                <% for(let rank = 1; rank <= 5; rank++) {%>
                    <% const identifier = `rank_${sound}_${rank}` %>
                    <li class="rank-box__item">
                        <% if(rank == 3) {%>
                            <input type="radio" id="<%= identifier %>" value="<%= rank %>"
                                   checked="checked" name="rank_<%= sound %>" class="rank-checkbox" />
                        <% } else {%>
                            <input type="radio" id="<%= identifier %>" value="<%= rank %>"
                                   name="rank_<%= sound %>" class="rank-checkbox" />
                        <% } %>
                        <label for="<%= identifier %>"><%= rank %></label>
                    </li>
                <% } %>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <% } %>
        </ul>
        <input type="submit" value="Send soundtrack ranking" />
    </form>
    <div class="footer">
        <h2>Technical stuff</h2>
        <p>Created by Petr Wudi as part of MI-MVI course at <a href="https://fit.cvut.cz">FIT ÄŒVUT</a>.</p>
        <p>You could access <a href="https://https://github.com/wudip/evolve-music" class="github-repo-link">Github
            repository</a> of the project.</p>
        <p>There is some technology under the hood created by people who published their work for free to use - namely
        <a href="https://github.com/grimmdude/MidiPlayerJS">MidiPlayerJS</a> and <a href="http://getskeleton.com">Skeleton</a>.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>